[{"ave_id":"AVE-2002-0001","file_name":"2002/AVE-2002-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2002-1131","title":"SquirrelMail 1.2.7 跨站脚本漏洞","description":"SquirrelMail 1.2.7 及更早版本中存在多个跨站脚本（XSS）漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 addressbook.php、options.php、search.php 或 help.php 等页面提交特制的恶意参数触发该漏洞，导致恶意脚本代码在其他用户的浏览器中执行，从而窃取会话 Cookie、劫持用户会话或冒充用户执行任意操作。攻击无需身份认证，仅需诱使用户点击特制链接即可触发，影响面较广。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2002-1131"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2002-10-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:58:47.023","remediation":"升级 SquirrelMail 至 1.2.8 或更高版本，该版本修复了 addressbook.php、options.php、search.php、help.php 等文件中的输入过滤缺失问题。同时建议在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）层面启用 mod_security 规则，对用户输入参数进行严格的 HTML 编码过滤，防范跨站脚本攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2002-09/0246.html","http://sourceforge.net/project/shownotes.php?group_id=311&release_id=110774","http://www.debian.org/security/2002/dsa-191","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/10145.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2002-204.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/5763","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21811","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2002/CVE-2002-1131.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2002/CVE-2002-1131.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/http/cves/2002/CVE-2002-1131.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/cve-2002-1131-1302.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-2002-1131_7.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2002/1xxx/CVE-2002-1131.json","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder3/cve-2002-1131-1303.yaml","https:/